node.text:
Sundays are for SOUND DESIGN! ⁣
⁣
⁣
Today’s video will break down the signature “Future Rave” sound by David Guetta and Morten!⁣
⁣
⁣
Learn the synth settings, post-processing, and FX that will get you close to this sound.⁣
⁣
⁣
I take my time explaining each step so you can apply these techniques / concepts to any synth, EQ, compressor, reverb, and delay! ⁣
⁣
⁣
If you like this idea of recreating signature sounds, let me know in the comments and I’m more than happy to do more! ♥️⁣
⁣
⁣

node.text:
Everyone is on their own timeline!⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣
Don’t compare yourself to other artists. Their path is their own.⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣
Sure, you can give me 100 examples of ppl that hit it big as a kid. ⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣
Or people that blew up really early on. ⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣
Those examples are the most talked about because they’re marketed that way. ⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣
But there are countless examples of ppl that took years and years and didn’t hit it til later on in life.⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣
There are also countless examples of artists who were other professions first! ⁣⁣⁣⁣
In Cosmic we talk about our students accomplishing huge results. ⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣
A lot of them are also Lawyers, Doctors, Engineers, Bartenders, Waitresses, etc!⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣
You’re on your own path. ⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣
Don’t compare yourself to others. ⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣
Keep going. ⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
